name: One-Bedroom-Suite-One-Bedroom-Suite---Kitchenette
caption: One Bedroom Suite - Kitchenette
description: This kitchenette includes a glass table with 4 chairs, refrigerator, microwave, sink, and dishwasher.
alt: On the right wall, the microwave is built into the cabinet above the refrigerator. To the left more cabinets hang above a dishwasher. In the middle of the room, a dining table sits surrounded by 3 armless chairs. On the left wall, a large window. Above the table, a light fixture hangs from the ceiling.
